high_descs: Go forward and the to the right to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the large knife up from the counter.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Put the knife back down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn around and cross the room and then go left to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the potato slice in the fridge and shut the door and then take the potato slice out and shut the fridge door again.
Go left and cross the room to stand in front of the microwave above the stove.
Put the potato slice in the microwave and shut the door and then take the potato out and shut the door again.
Turn around and cross the room and then turn left to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the potato slice in the fridge and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled and heated potato slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Head to the white table in front of you, at the table take a right and walk to the counter top that is on the left of the stove
Pick up the knife that is sitting on the counter top behind the soap bottles
Slice the potato that is sitting behind the soap bottles
Place the knife on the counter to the right of the soap bottles
Pick up a slice of the potato
Turn around and cross the room, take a left at the wall and walk to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the slice of potato inside on the bottom shelf to the left of the whole potato and then close the door. Then open the door and pick up the potato and close the door
Turn around and head toward the table across the room, hang a right and walk to the microwave above the stove
Open the microwave and place the slice of potato inside to the right, then close the microwave door and turn it on. Open the microwave and pick up the slice of potato
Turn around, cross the room, then hang left and walk to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the potato inside on the bottom shelf to the left of the whole potato and then close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato into a fridge

high_descs: Walk across the room to the counter on the lefthand side of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Set the knife down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Make your way across the room to the fridge.
Chill the potato in the fridge, taking it back out when you're done.
Turn left to walk to the microwave.
Heat up the potato slice in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn right to walk to the fridge.
Set the potato slice down in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato slice to heat it up in the microwave, putting it away in the fridge.
